Author: averybluebitch
Text: God, I feel ya. Yesterday my bf was super excited because we went to the drugstore and he weighted himself at -ghasp!- 51kg. Last time I weighted that was probably in middle school.

Author: lykaeria
Text: I have a friend who’s 94 lbs and is always trying to gain weight but can’t. Goddamn it I WISH we could switch places
